            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S.) In die martis qui est quinto die intrante mense octubris, presencia
                            <persName key="#Bishops #Witness #Ordinatio" ref="#people/2157"
                            >Ubaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Bishops" ref="#places/275">Mantuani</placeName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness #Ordinatio" ref="#people/2185">Ubaldi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudicis</rs> et <persName
                            key="#childOf #Witness #Ordinatio"><name ref="Azo"
                            >Azonis</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filii</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Hubaldus/de Parma"
                            >Ubaldi</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/53"
                            >Parma</placeName> et <persName key="#Witness #Ordinatio"><name
                                ref="Crispus/de Mandrio">Crispi</name></persName> de <placeName
                            ref="#places/2951">Mandria</placeName> et filiorum <persName
                            key="#parentOf"><name ref="Rotius/de Pelavo">Rozonis</name></persName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/2950">Pelavo</placeName> et alios quam plurium,
                        dedit <rs key="#Countess">comitissa</rs>
                        <persName
                            key="#Countess #Palatium #Churches #Decima #Castle #Curtes #Fruits/vegetables"
                            ref="#people/125">Matilda</persName>
                        <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">proprietario iure</rs>
                        <rs key="#Palatium">palacium</rs> de <placeName
                            key="#Palatium #Churches #Castle #Curtes" ref="#places/1506">Castro
                            Ariano</placeName>, concessit <rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Decima" ref="#juridical_persons/2082">Sancti
                            Prosperii</orgName> sitam in eodem <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Decima">decima</rs> ad eandem ecclesiam pertinente, cum <geogName
                            key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/2078"><rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curte</rs></geogName> et accessionem et ubi <rs
                            key="#Fruits/vegetables">ortus</rs> exscolitur insimul tenente.
                        Concessit etiam ecclesiam <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2084">Sancti Donnini</orgName> sitam in
                            <placeName key="#Mountains #Churches" ref="#places/2949"><rs
                                key="#Mountains">munte</rs> Ville</placeName> et ecclesiam <orgName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2085">Sancti Prosperii</orgName>
                        et ecclesiam <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/2086">Sancti
                            Gregori</orgName> de <placeName key="#Churches" ref="#places/2910"
                            >Antognano</placeName> cum omnibus possesionibus ad eas ecclesias
                        pertinentibus, salvo canonico iure <orgName key="#Mother_churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/108"><placeName key="#Mother_churches"
                                ref="#places/191">Regensis</placeName> ecclesie</orgName>, favente
                        et specialiter consenciente <persName key="#Bishops" ref="#people/2184"
                            >Heriberto</persName> Regense episcopo, <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries #Abbots #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Palatium #Churches #Decima #Castle #Curtes #Fruits/vegetables"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/2001">Sancti Benedicti sito iuxta
                            Padum</orgName> in quo monasterio <persName key="#Abbots"
                            ref="#people/2163">Vuilelmus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abas</rs> eo tempore preerat; qui prefatus abas de
                        monasterio suo propter persecucionem <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/77">Einrici</persName>
                        <rs key="#Emperor/king">tiranni</rs> congregacionem fugiens apud predictam
                        comitissam in montanis sustentatus est. Que misericordia ducta ad
                        sustentacionem fratrum hec omnia que in hanc cartulam continentur predicto
                        monasterio in perpetuum concessit cum consensu sicut dictum est Regensis
                        episcopi, sine omni eidem Matilde conmitisse vel sui heredes contradicionem
                        vel repeticionem. Factum est hoc anno ab incarnacione domini nostri Iesu
                        Christi millesimo nonagesimo secundo, indicione quintadecima. Actum
                            <placeName ref="#places/2902">Carpeneta</placeName> feliciter. <persName
                            key="#Witness #Ordinatio"><name ref="Hugo/de Rodilia"
                            >Ugo</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2952"
                            >Rodilia</placeName>, <persName key="#Witness #Ordinatio"
                            ref="#people/2187">Nordino</persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2953"
                            >Gaio</placeName>, <persName key="#Witness #Ordinatio"
                            ref="#people/2186">Ubaldinus</persName> de Carpeneta qui interfuerunt
                            <rs key="#Witness">testes</rs>. (S.) Ego <persName
                                key="#Writer #Notary #Ordinatio" ref="#people/3760">Guido</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> Sacri Palacii interfui et hanc <rs
                            key="#Ordinatio">cartulam concessionem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
